Pant departs after a bit of drama

commentary: Mohammed Shami to Warner, FOUR runs places this past mid-off, and lets out a celebratory yelp. The batsmen embrace, and this one is done and dusted! Australia do it in stye, with the highest partnership for any wicket in ODI cricket against India!
